---
title: Roasted Pesto Chicken with Italian Panzanella
description: Panzanella is a classic Tuscan dish best enjoyed in the warmer months. Created for the purpose of using up stale bread, it’s a dish with humble roots. Together with fresh summer veggies and pesto chicken, we’re transforming this modest dish to something worthy of company!
